---
import { ExternalLink, Github, Star, GitBranch, Users, MessageCircle, Link } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<section id="collaboration" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Colaboraciones</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Aquí tienen algunos de los proyectos en los que he colaborado como desarrollador en
                estos años.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <article
                class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow overflow-hidden group"
            >
                <div
                    class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-blue-400 flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                    <img src="/logo/auj.webp" alt="Logo de AdoptaUnJunior" class="w-48 h-48" />
                </div>

                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">AdoptaUnJunior</h3>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 min-h-36">
                        Junto a otros desarrolladores ayudamos a la organización sin ánimo de lucro
                        AdoptaUnJunior a realizar su web.
                    </p>

                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            React
                        </span>
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            NextJS
                        </span>
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            TypeScript
                        </span>

                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            TailwindCSS
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mt-6">
                        <a
                            href="https://adoptaunjunior.es/"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                            class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors"
                            aria-label="URL de la web"
                        >
                            <Link size={18} />
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium">Web</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article
                class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow overflow-hidden group"
            >
                <div
                    class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800 to-black flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                    <img src="/logo/mymedesp.webp" alt="Logo de Mymedesp" class="p-4" />
                </div>

                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Mymedesp</h3>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 min-h-36">
                        Colaboré junto a unos amigos en el desarrollo de la web y la app para la
                        gestión de recetas y menús.
                    </p>

                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            React
                        </span>
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            Astro
                        </span>
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            TypeScript
                        </span>
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            Supabase
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mt-6">
                        <a
                            href="https://mymedesp.com/"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                            class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors"
                            aria-label="URL de la web"
                        >
                            <Link size={18} />
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium">Web</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article
                class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow overflow-hidden group"
            >
                <div
                    class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-red-600 flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/logo/charactersvault.webp"
                        alt="Logo de Characters Vault"
                        class="w-34 h-34"
                    />
                </div>

                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Chraracters Vault</h3>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 min-h-36">
                        Contribuí como fullstack developer en el desarrollo de Characters Vault, una
                        plataforma de gestión de personajes para FoundryVTT.
                    </p>

                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            React
                        </span>
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            TypeScript
                        </span>
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            Mobx
                        </span>
                        <span
                            class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
                        >
                            Supabase
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mt-6">
                        <a
                            href="https://charactersvault.com/"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                            class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors"
                            aria-label="URL de la web"
                        >
                            <Link size={18} />
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium">Web</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
